main event: A white object was observed flying erratically at 25,000 feet and brightening before disappearing over the horizon.
interesting points: The sighting lasted for 10 minutes and was confirmed by five watchstanders., The object was first observed at a ten-degree elevation and bearing 195T., It was visually observed with binoculars by a reliable witness., The object appeared as bright as the first magnitude star., The sighting was reported during night time.
